12:41.011 --> 12:43.264
like we used to do when we
were kinda freaky, you know?

12:43.347 --> 12:45.849
The freaky Freelings
on the road again!

12:45.933 --> 12:48.686
You know, the family
whose house disappeared!

12:48.769 --> 12:50.813
Watch them find it, Diane.

12:50.896 --> 12:52.273
I'm not going to
get upset about this,

12:52.356 --> 12:53.816
