<i>Would be sad if our new love...</i>

14:37.628 --> 14:39.630
Am I interrupting again?

14:40.047 --> 14:41.090
Hi.

14:41.799 --> 14:43.092
Hi, pumpkin.

14:43.175 --> 14:45.511
Mom, I'm going
to be a ballerina.

14:46.428 --> 14:47.388
Great.

14:47.471 --> 14:49.223
Not tonight, honey.

14:50.432 --> 14:52.226
Bedtime. Say,
"Good night, Mom."

14:52.309 --> 14:53.352
Good night, honey.

14:53.435 --> 14:55.062
Let's sleep in our own
bed tonight, shall we?

14:55.145 --> 14:56.105
Okay.

14:56.188 --> 14:57.898
<i>We're dancing down to my bed</i>

14:57.981 --> 14:59.566
