15:20.170 --> 15:22.172
Uh, no, sweetheart.
E. Buzz would get upset.

15:22.256 --> 15:24.007
Robbie, come on.
Why?

15:24.091 --> 15:26.093
Well, he's not used to
having other pets around.

15:26.176 --> 15:27.428
Robert!

15:27.511 --> 15:29.888
How would you like it if
I brought home a new baby?

15:29.972 --> 15:32.266
That's even better
than a kitten.

15:32.349 --> 15:34.268
Mom, I have a great idea.

15:34.351 --> 15:36.937
No, we are not buying
a television set, Robert.

15:37.020 --> 15:39.398
Mom, a present
for Dad. It's a bargain.

15:48.991 --> 15:50.033
Mom!

15:51.034 --> 15:52.077
Mom!

15:55.998 --> 15:58.459
Mom, where are you? Mom!

16:05.549 --> 16:07.050
Mom! Mom!

16:07.259 --> 16:08.469
Robbie!

16:10.304 --> 16:11.388
Mom!

16:16.560 --> 16:17.728
Robbie!

16:20.105 --> 16:21.148
Hi.

16:22.232 --> 16:23.275
Hi.

16:23.692 --> 16:25.694
Are you lost, sweetheart?

16:27.154 --> 16:29.031
Are you afraid, honey?

16:30.407 --> 16:32.826
Well, why don't
you come with me?

16:32.910 --> 16:33.911
No.

16:35.078 --> 16:36.413
All right.

16:37.039 --> 16:41.418
I'll sing you a song
till your mommy comes back.

16:42.461 --> 16:47.925
<i>God is in his holy temple</i>

16:48.759 --> 16:53.180
<i>Earthly thoughts be silent now</i>

16:53.764 --> 16:54.890
I'd like
to purchase this.

16:54.973 --> 16:57.726
Okay,
that's $10.26 plus tax.

16:58.894 --> 17:00.687
Where's Carol Anne?

17:00.771 --> 17:03.065
I don't know.
She was just here.

17:04.691 --> 17:06.359
Carol Anne?

17:07.236 --> 17:08.319
Baby!

17:10.739 --> 17:13.200
<i>He is with us...</i>

17:13.282 --> 17:16.244
Carol Anne. Honey, what happened?
Did you get lost'?

17:16.328 --> 17:17.788
I don't know.

17:18.622 --> 17:19.623
Thank you.

17:19.705 --> 17:21.124
My pleasure.

17:21.415 --> 17:24.169
Such a lovely child.

17:24.252 --> 17:26.128
Oh, thank you so much.

17:28.715 --> 17:31.385
I'm sorry, honey.
We just stopped into a shop.

17:31.468 --> 17:34.096
I thought you were
right there with us.

17:40.477 --> 17:42.187
Honey, what is it?

17:42.271 --> 17:45.315
Mom, I want to go home.

17:46.024 --> 17:48.777
- They're very unusual.
- They're just drawings.

17:50.279 --> 17:51.488
Ugly.
Aw.

17:52.614 --> 17:54.575
You know that she can see
colors with her hands.

17:54.658 --> 17:57.578
Mama, we don't want
to hear that stuff, okay?

17:57.953 --> 18:00.414
And we don't want Carol
Anne to hear, most of all.

18:00.497 --> 18:02.833
There's nothing to be afraid of.

18:03.041 --> 18:06.295
How do you know what we should be
afraid of? You weren't there, were you?

18:06.378 --> 18:08.630
Why don't you tell me?
It might help.

18:08.714 --> 18:09.756
I did tell you.

18:09.840 --> 18:10.799
No, not everything.

18:10.882 --> 18:12.801
I don't remember everything.

18:31.194 --> 18:34.197
Well, first the canary died.

18:37.743 --> 18:40.537
And then the chairs
went all funny.

18:41.330 --> 18:44.416
And I thought it was kind
of exciting, you know?

18:44.916 --> 18:46.293
And then...

18:47.753 --> 18:49.546
Carol Anne was gone.

18:52.549 --> 18:53.759
And I...

19:07.189 --> 19:08.857
Honey, what is it?

19:09.983 --> 19:11.234
Nothing.

19:15.739 --> 19:19.284
Nothing. I just want to get
on with our lives. It's over.

19:19.618 --> 19:20.786
Diane.

19:21.620 --> 19:25.248
Diane, you've got to go
unafraid into this life.

19:25.540 --> 19:27.918
You don't want to instill
fear into that child

19:28.001 --> 19:30.253
who is truly gifted and
filled with knowledge.

19:30.337 --> 19:32.047
I don't want her to be gifted!

19:32.130 --> 19:33.882
You don't mean that.

19:33.965 --> 19:36.385
I'm going to bed,
Mama. Good night.

19:40.847 --> 19:43.058
I'll be there if you need me.

21:21.448 --> 21:22.532
Yes?

21:23.992 --> 21:25.035
Yes.

21:26.161 --> 21:27.621
I'll be good.

21:29.706 --> 21:31.333
I love you, too.

21:33.084 --> 21:34.878
Good night, Gramma.

21:44.346 --> 21:45.972
She knew you loved her so much.

21:46.056 --> 21:48.683
Oh, if I just had one more day.

21:59.069 --> 22:00.570
What's wrong?

22:04.908 --> 22:06.117
Honey...

22:10.080 --> 22:12.332
Gramma passed away last night.

22:12.749 --> 22:14.251
Gramma died?

22:18.713 --> 22:20.298
Come here, baby.

22:28.807 --> 22:30.600
It's all right, Mom.

22:45.907 --> 22:48.159
<i>Let's plant
them over there, okay?</i>

22:48.743 --> 22:51.204
<i>All right, now, what do you think?
Do you want it here?</i>

22:51.288 --> 22:52.289
<i>No.</i>

22:53.582 --> 22:55.208
How about here?

22:55.292 --> 22:56.418
No.
Where?

22:56.501 --> 22:58.128
I want it there, right there.

22:58.211 --> 22:59.629
Right there?

22:59.921 --> 23:01.965
Right there.
Absolutely here.

23:02.048 --> 23:03.425
Okay.

23:03.967 --> 23:06.845
You dig a hole.
Dig it very deep.

23:17.898 --> 23:19.149
Oh, Mom.

23:21.192 --> 23:23.486
You always made me feel so safe.

23:32.871 --> 23:34.623
I love you so much.

23:42.505 --> 23:43.590
Mom?

23:47.719 --> 23:51.431
