23:54.059 --> 23:56.978
Darling, you can be
anything you want to be.

24:07.530 --> 24:08.823
Diane.

24:08.907 --> 24:10.951
Mama?
Diane.

24:15.705 --> 24:16.665
Help me!

24:16.748 --> 24:17.791
Oh!

24:21.378 --> 24:22.754
Help me!

24:27.801 --> 24:28.802
Help me!

26:15.325 --> 26:16.743
